 since going public three years ago after a SPAC merger. The company=E2=80=
=99s
stock dropped 11 percent on its first day of trading, and has fallen 89 per=
cent since. It has a current market value of $165 million.

The question now is whether BuzzFeed Inc. can continue to operate outside o=
f bankruptcy or absent a debt restructuring of some sort. The trouble start=
