 I=E2=80=99m <b>Bill Cohan</b>, back in Manhattan for a moment to dip into =
a few holiday parties=E2=80=94particularly the <b>Tony Fratto </b>extravaga=
nza in Tribeca, near Puck=E2=80=99s airy HQ.<br/><br/>In tonight=E2=80=99s =
