p at Sotheby=E2=80=99s following a nearly $1 billion investment from ADQ. P=
lus, <b>Eriq Gardner </b>has some insights on the changing M&amp;A landscap=
e, and <b>John Ourand </b>offers some of the backstory on <b>Steve Cohen</b=
>=E2=80=99s latest investment. <br/><br/><i>But first, a few words on BuzzF=
eed=E2=80=99s potential bankruptcy=E2=80=A6</i><br/></p>
